{"tid":2490102,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"四大本地YouTube頻道下周首次聯乘直播 網民率先比拼16大女神","createTime":"2021-04-15T10:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T12:20:21.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b673c4e3aa729eb42e2e311cac67ec4cf5416955","tid":2490102,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZLI1zGKn8wRSxTAC07tP_ezx11Q=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2D4WDSPLVRC27KZMQ34SKY32MQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZLI1zGKn8wRSxTAC07tP_ezx11Q%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2D4WDSPLVRC27KZMQ34SKY32MQ.jpg&h=44f4e2d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四個本地YouTube Channel「試當真」、「FHProductionHK熊仔頭」 、「啱Channel」與「小薯茄」早前在網上宣佈聯乘企劃，下星期二（4月20日）將舉行四台聯合網上直播，不少網民對此表示期待。有網民在討論區發起「香港四台YouTube 女神外表排行榜 」，把四個頻道的女神分為八級，當中熊仔頭的Santis Chan位列榜首，被評為R（rare）級激罕女神，小薯茄麗英排於榜末，被評為Ｆ級女神。其餘女神排名分別是S級的阿冰（吳冰）、Jessica（陳苡臻）、米露迪；Ａ級的Ah Gi（樊沛珈）、嘉盈及童童（蔡曉童）；B級有杜小喬與Jackie；C級是SuperGirls成員陳穎欣（Yanny）及阿慈（倪安慈）；Me Chan（陳逸敏 ）被評為D級。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DJ69dWVEdo-O3gq8CUa3_XoYRiQ=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MLW3OBJ2DRA7BD7SZS2BSUOMQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDJ69dWVEdo-O3gq8CUa3_XoYRiQ%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMLW3OBJ2DRA7BD7SZS2BSUOMQE.jpg&h=494c87a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此榜在討論區發酵一日，已獲近1,500位網民投票，但正評僅得逾30票，不少網民似乎不認同女神排名，亦有網民指發帖者未有列出所有女神，結果不公。有網民把女神們重新排列，並仔細列出各女神優劣點，當中Ah Gi由Ａ級升為Ｓ級，網民大讚她有內容、有性格、靚女、聰明兼搞笑，杜小喬及Yanny分別為Ａ及Ｂ級，網民直言兩人在眾女神中年紀較大，難以與青春無敵的「妹妹」比拼，Santis Chan由榜首直插Ｃ級，認為她雖然青春兼靚女，但是冇內涵。<br />\n<br />\n其實16位女神各有各支持者，剛剛推出新歌《矮妹正傳》的麗英談論度極高，獲不少fans力撐，她在IG以「全死角美少女」自居，有12萬人追蹤，但有網民認為她不夠靚亦沒有身材，稱不上是女神。與麗英同樣來自小薯茄的吳冰，亦引起網民激辯，不少網民覺得她只是普通女仔，平日打扮亦流露港女味，有網民戲稱她是與電影《賭俠》中飾演大軍的程東撞樣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9umbRCr1zlmRcpVh-aZzZ3EoZQU=/802x533/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OSVJS2SJD5H47BTE4MWTZTVXFQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9umbRCr1zlmRcpVh-aZzZ3EoZQU%3D%2F802x533%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOSVJS2SJD5H47BTE4MWTZTVXFQ.jpg&h=cf454818&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6WfSVI5qUKX5WKSYD4od4tThZss=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YXHT4GXXONDU3P5JFB3KDK47MI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6WfSVI5qUKX5WKSYD4od4tThZss%3D%2F802x1002%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYXHT4GXXONDU3P5JFB3KDK47MI.jpg&h=f774a3af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳冰、麗英與童童三人都是小薯茄成員，有留言狠批三人是「豬扒」：「小薯茄嗰三件根本豬扒，比到盡都係叫普通女仔。即係食飯坐你隔籬台都冇興趣望嗰種劣質港女，人哋拍片全部有劇本你都當係性格。 」有網民為她們平反謂：「我識好多人鍾意阿冰都有課金」、「Ah Gi、阿慈無可能高過阿冰，睇阿冰嗰條二選一，同最新個條雪櫃冷笑話，真心戀愛feel 」、「童童正喎 但唔會課金」、「我愛麗英」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JreneHYcb0DdPC7wLJh5AwDXrYY=/802x802/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/242PLWXN7NDU3PY4DER6I7D25A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJreneHYcb0DdPC7wLJh5AwDXrYY%3D%2F802x802%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F242PLWXN7NDU3PY4DER6I7D25A.jpg&h=f71e1c3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fY-BaC3mKSQAtFQUsQnw3uegqqQ=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ODOOPCRF4FB77KZGNACFMDCO7U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfY-BaC3mKSQAtFQUsQnw3uegqqQ%3D%2F802x1002%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FODOOPCRF4FB77KZGNACFMDCO7U.jpg&h=e8b6ffff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/v-7OCVcMTJQdtqSghjAzBvT0iDk=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DMOH2K4JONAF5MWLSQK7XPWS3Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fv-7OCVcMTJQdtqSghjAzBvT0iDk%3D%2F802x1002%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDMOH2K4JONAF5MWLSQK7XPWS3Y.jpg&h=84800947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱Channel的劉展翹（Jackie）有「少女毛舜筠 」之稱，同樣不是標準美女，但有個性的打扮深得網民喜愛。剛加盟的熊仔頭Santis Chan被封為「港大楊恭如」，今年20歲的她是正宗00後，IG雖然只有13個帖文，但已獲逾3萬人追蹤。她早前在熊仔頭網絡影片《第三者故事》中擔任女主角，演技幼嫩，但眼大大、帶點混血兒feel的甜美外貌相當吸睛，不少網民在她IG留言打氣鼓勵。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/It4loWSRKHbXiXfaESCkKdta3EI=/802x983/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OUYXD2563NGPXMII24GMEWMJ3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIt4loWSRKHbXiXfaESCkKdta3EI%3D%2F802x983%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOUYXD2563NGPXMII24GMEWMJ3M.jpg&h=acab922f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qR4SH7oEmnIGTS4DGZUmFFslUN8=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QJUSKPNNBJDMBAK577MY2642JI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqR4SH7oEmnIGTS4DGZUmFFslUN8%3D%2F802x1002%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQJUSKPNNBJDMBAK577MY2642JI.jpg&h=e230e38f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CmpjLD2kXbOV-CK5kV9GUIoiR5E=/802x1001/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PY66K4WTEBC7FEU4WMXMIIIRSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCmpjLD2kXbOV-CK5kV9GUIoiR5E%3D%2F802x1001%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPY66K4WTEBC7FEU4WMXMIIIRSY.jpg&h=0d61f8cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2UT5oMZMgxjPHtDBLbV33wb-Sno=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Q2N4R2ZQBJHCJNGZR5BZTTDLIM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2UT5oMZMgxjPHtDBLbV33wb-Sno%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQ2N4R2ZQBJHCJNGZR5BZTTDLIM.jpg&h=a5600353&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HeqehpWox2gylDNgF5N0UQ_x1fA=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DS5EM6EZ4NAUVFUY5YL6S4FP4Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHeqehpWox2gylDNgF5N0UQ_x1fA%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDS5EM6EZ4NAUVFUY5YL6S4FP4Y.jpg&h=0f5a2c56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/f-KklvNvob-HemOzkblGxwfr47Q=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JO23SM6A2ZHUPPFNLD7AQTB45E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ff-KklvNvob-HemOzkblGxwfr47Q%3D%2F802x1002%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJO23SM6A2ZHUPPFNLD7AQTB45E.jpg&h=b514e3ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210415/VPK7BZEDTZGGNCF3WP3B47VYNM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210415%2FVPK7BZEDTZGGNCF3WP3B47VYNM%2F&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwBfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=5dfb1fd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210415%2FVPK7BZEDTZGGNCF3WP3B47VYNM%2F&h=ef7fd218\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210415/VPK7BZEDTZGGNCF3WP3B47VYNM/</a>"},{"pid":"287cd5d826f491a32fccbfd786828c511f637899","tid":2490102,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:49:02.000Z","msg":"以為講緊咩cup，心諗明明d女無咁大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e3a43d8ee38eafe1f9169c3ef0a903ad42e7dc","tid":2490102,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:16:03.000Z","msg":"Ah Gi。呀 me"},{"pid":"3b1abfd3d8acc372d10058b3ef9acc996a7750a3","tid":2490102,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:20:22.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"e173feb57470f9cd731aa45cf1d482a56ece4d7e","tid":2490102,"uid":165136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:21:52.000Z","msg":"童B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e38f2cec01ee36788da58f14ab54be1435ac58","tid":2490102,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:32:23.000Z","msg":"我個po負皮多係因為眾口難調<br />\n個個排位都唔同，一有唔同就負皮架啦<br />\n但我個榜係經九次對決票數而得出，公平公正囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb036737c93b3c377847454597a9f122cf6a497","tid":2490102,"uid":161190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:00:06.000Z","msg":"全部都係雞 可以問價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754f993c5c396bfe41906dc03f2a949db2e12795","tid":2490102,"uid":161190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdb036737c93b3c377847454597a9f122cf6a497","tid":2490102,"uid":161190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:00:06.000Z","msg":"全部都係雞 可以問價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:00:43.000Z","msg":"除咗麗英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2eb4020202a223074152c6fd8e91d18da6be0e","tid":2490102,"uid":15501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:20:21.000Z","msg":"點解YANNY會咁低分"}]}